1. What happened to My Computer? Your important files are encrypted. Many of your documents, photos, videos, databases and other files are no longer accessible because they have been encrypted. Maybe you are busy looking for a way to recover them, but do not waste your time. Nobody can recover your files without payment.
2. Recover My Files? Can I recover My files? You can decrypt some of your files for free! Try now by clicking 'Decrypt'. Also, if you don't pay in 7 days, you won't be able to recover your files forever.
3. How do I pay? Check the current price of 'For information, click 'How to buy Cryptocurrency'. After your payment, click 'Check Payment' to start the decryption process.
